      "para_id": "Q001657.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built his tempel of Bagara ."
    }
